<i>noun</i>: 순례 [술례] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>순례 [술례]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pilgrimage</dd><br>
<dd>종교가 처음 일어난 곳이나 성인의 무덤 등 종교적으로 의미가 있는 곳을 찾아다니며 참배함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of visiting places of religious significance such as the place where a religion was founded, a saint's grave, etc., and paying respects.</dd><br>
<dd>2. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 여러 곳을 찾아다니며 방문함.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The act of visiting many places.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>